# Dosbox

- Ripping full CD's

cdrdao read-cd --datafile image.bin --driver generic-mmc:0x20000 --device /dev/cdrom --read-raw image.toc
toc2cue image.toc image.cue

- And then mount it:

IMGMOUNT <drive letter> <cue file> -t iso

- You can mount multiple ones

IMGMOUNT <drive letter> <cue file 1> <cue file 2> ... <cue file n> -t iso

and then use CTRL-F4 to switch them


# ScummVM

apt-get install scummvm beneath-a-steel-sky flight-of-the-amazon-queen
